data.description: PRICE REDUCED! Absolutely Charming 2 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms villa in the desirable gated Country Club community of Forest Grove at Indian Spring! No Mandatory Membership! Walk into a welcoming foyer to the tiled living room featuring solar skylights. Brand new 2023 AC! A tastefully updated kitchen featuring granite counter tops, backsplash, wood cabinets and solar skylights. Sliding doors in the living room and dining room open up to the inviting enclosed air conditioned & tiled Florida Room, ideal for entertaining. The ample Master Bedroom features a beautifully updated Master Bathroom, a Walk-In Closet plus an additional closet. Other features: chair railing in the hallway, crown molding in the Master, newer high quality blinds, plantation shutters, accordion shutters. It will not last!
